QuestData.Title: Schematic Reassimilation: Pale Regal Cervid
QuestData.Description:
<This schematic contains the pattern of a new protoform construct. Present it to an appropriate protoform forge and it may instantiate one of these creatures for you.>
<The Enlightened of Pilgrim's Grace likely know where such a forge can be found.>
QuestData.LogDescription: Present the schematic to an appropriate protoform forge.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Present the schematic to an appropriate protoform forge in Zereth Mortis.
